<div class="com-share" data-id="16385" data-title="《苹果向广告开战，这会改变广告业吗？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16385/medium/16385.jpg?1445410767" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16385.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
